`( ... ++ (tl[0]. ++ ... ++ tl[idx'-1]. ++ l1) ++ ... ).insertIdx (hd.length + sum + l1.length) elt = ... ++ (tl[0]. ++ ... ++ tl[idx'-1]. ++ l1) ++ [elt] ++ ...), which is what we have in `(hd ++ (tl[0]. ++ ... ++ tl[idx'-1]. ++ (l1 ++ [elt]) ++ ...`.

