### Formal Derivation

First, recall that:

`(hd ++ (tl.set idx' (l1 ++ [elt])).flatten) = hd ++ (tl[0]. ++ ... ++ tl[idx'-1]. ++ (l1 ++ [elt]) ++ tl[idx'+1]. ++ ...)`.

`(hd ++ (tl.set idx' l1).flatten) = hd ++ (tl[0]. ++ ... ++ tl[idx'-1]. ++ l1 ++ tl[idx'+1]. ++ ...)`.

